{{!
    @template mod_booking/form_booking_options_selector_suggestion

    Moodle template for the list of valid options in an autocomplate form element.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * id int user id
    * firstname string user's first name
    * lastname string user's last name
    * email string user email field

    Example context (json):
    {
        "id": 1,
        "titleprefix": "123",
        "text": "Name of the Booking option",
        "instancename": "Bookinginstance 1"
    }
}}
<span>
    <span class="booking-option-suggestion font-weight-bold">
        {{#titleprefix}}{{.}} - {{/titleprefix}}{{text}}<small> ID: {{id}}</small>
    </span>
    <div><small>{{instancename}}</small></div>
</span>
